subs.text: Busy day programming. I'm doing well. Lite blogging day. :smile:
I have to admit that I like cats. People think they don't have a sense of humor, but they do.
This is a test. For the next sixty seconds this station will conduct a test of the blog posting system. Not an emergency.
I'll leave you with this question. Where is the Resistance?

One more thing. Why isn't Michael Moore on MSNBC, give him an hour on Saturday. It would be the most watched program they have. Call it Michael Moore tells you the truth about what's actually going on, and what you should do. It could be a call-in show. My first question for him would be, how can I help the Resistance?
